extends layout
block content
  .carousel-inner(role='listbox')
    .carousel-item.active
      img.first-slide(src='https://www.walldevil.com/wallpapers/w09/children-who-chase-lost-voices-makoto-shinkai-anime.jpg', alt='Banner')
      .container
        .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block.text-left
          h1 AniMate
          p
            | A global network for anime lovers all round, the anime matchmaking site of your dreams.  So good it'll make your heart go doki doki.
          br
          p
            | "It's honestly the best website, I find all my super hot model girlfriends on here." - Leonardo Dicaprio.
          p
            a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary(href='/about', role='button') Learn More
    br
    br
    .container.marketing
      .row.featurette
        .col-md-7
          h2.featurette-heading What is AniMate?
          p.lead
            | AniMate believes that compatibility is key when finding
            | a partner or friend. If you're tired of going onto endless dates only
            | to return home to your body pillow every night then we're the site
            | for you. Say good-bye to judgemental girls or shallow guys. At AniMate
            | anyone and everyone is equal. Finally connect with people who share
            | your weird niche views and hobbies!
        .col-md-5
          img.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='http://68.media.tumblr.com/531ab774a5bf34d887dee52bdf520fce/tumblr_inline_n6l3p3MXsU1s13368.jpg', alt='Generic placeholder image')
      hr.featurette-divider
      .row.featurette
        .col-md-7.push-md-5
          h2.featurette-heading
            | How does it work?
            span.text-muted  See for yourself.
          p.lead
            | Through the use of our special matching algorithm users
            | can find fellow members with the same anime interests. You can
            | simply browse through pre-exsting members using our search function
            | but the ability to edit your own interests or appear in other people's
            |searches is only available to registered users.
        .col-md-5.pull-md-7
          img.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='http://www.nextadvisor.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/online-dating-pickup-lines.jpg', alt='Generic placeholder image')
      hr.featurette-divider
      .row.featurette
        .col-md-7
          h2.featurette-heading
            | Interested?
            span.text-muted  Here's a more in-depth look
          p.lead
            | You can enter up to 3 animes in the search function to view
            | the top 10 candidates within our vast database of members. You will
            | be privy to their username, name and age. You cannot message them
            |until you have become a registered member though.
            |After registering with us and entering your 3 anime of choice,
            | you be asked to log into your account again. From there you will have
            | access to your profile page where you can change and update your
            |information as you please.
        .col-md-5
          img.featurette-image.img-fluid.mx-auto(src='https://fthmb.tqn.com/JqrBswIAKAhso2KkrnA5IkYfts8=/4910x3472/filters:fill(auto,1)/about/question_mark-166836001-56af9f3c3df78cf772c6c639.jpg', alt='Generic placeholder image')
